text: Eunidia transversefasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning and Jong in 1941.BioLib.cz - Eunidia transversefasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1941
